---
/**
 * Section 2: The Problem
 * Centered text block, empathy-driven copy. CSS scroll-driven fade-ins.
 */
---

<section aria-label="The reality" class="bg-brand-background py-section">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[44rem] px-lg md:px-2xl">
    <h2 class="sr-only">The reality you live every day</h2>

    <p class="reveal-on-scroll font-body text-body-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-brand-primary">
      You run the calendar. You manage the meals, the logistics, the emotional labor of everyone around you.
    </p>

    <p class="reveal-on-scroll-delayed mt-3xl font-body text-body-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-brand-primary">
      When someone asks what you need, you don't even know where to start.
    </p>

    <p class="reveal-on-scroll-delayed mt-3xl font-heading text-h3 font-medium italic leading-snug text-brand-primary">
      Calaire exists for that moment. The one where you stop managing and start breathing.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
